rComments: Great prof! It's important to go to class since she explains better and puts blanks in the notes online, but if you go to class, you can fill in the blanks and those are usually questions on the exam. The subject was very interesting.

Good prof ans in this class her axams was easy. She's really interesting

Amazing teacher, one of the best i've ever had. Very clear, uses really good examples to explain, very helpful and obviously knows her stuff. Super tough midterms though. Overall I really liked her, and if given the chance i'll take her again. :)
